node.text: Happy Birthday to my twin Aunt & Uncle Commelita & Commodus (Man & Lita)‼️ Turnt the BIG60 today‼️ I love y'all & thank you for all the love,laughs, & hard taught lessons of life over the years. All we got is US... & that's all we ever needed‼️ Hate we missed the party but serves you right being born on our anniversary...😤the nerve😒 side bar*my boy Man definitely look like he ate boogers and flicked em on people back then 🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣
